results.name: Denominator the polynomial A_l(x) = sum_{d=1..l-1} x^(l-d)/d for index l=2n+1 evaluated at x=16.
comment: For numerators see A145639. For general properties of A_l(x) see A145609.
mathematica: m = 16; aa = {}; Do[k = 0; Do[k = k + m^(2 r + 1 - d)/d, {d, 1, 2 r}]; AppendTo[aa, Denominator[k]], {r, 1, 30}]; aa (*Artur Jasinski*)
results.author: _Artur Jasinski_, Oct 14 2008
